{"analytics_identifier":"PB1232","base_path":"/government/organisations/homes-england","content_id":"ad6f059a-f36c-48eb-a07f-4a6856f08f7f","description":"As the government’s housing and regeneration agency we believe that affordable, quality homes in well-designed places are key to improving people’s lives. Together with our partners, we’re accelerating the pace of house building and regeneration across the country, as we seek to deliver homes and places people are proud to live in – for generations to come. Homes England is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government , supported by 1 public body .","details":{"acronym":"Homes England","alternative_format_contact_email":"enquiries@homesengland.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>As the government’s housing and regeneration agency we believe that affordable, quality homes in well-designed places are key to improving people’s lives.</p>\n\n<p>Together with our partners, we’re accelerating the pace of house building and regeneration across the country, as we seek to deliver homes and places people are proud to live in – for generations to come.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Homes England\">Homes England</abbr> is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/ministry-of-housing-communities-local-government\">Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government</a>, supported by <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations#homes-england\">1 public body</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"ministry-of-housing-communities-local-government","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69bbc98d4b1db2e4ba9b6444/s960_Homes_England_Logo_Transparent_GOVUK.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69bbc98d4c478213a823cdf6/s300_Homes_England_Logo_Transparent_GOVUK.png"},"foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Homes England"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/homes-england/about/accessible-documents-policy","title":"Accessible documents policy"},{"href":"/government/organisations/homes-england/about/complaints-procedure","title":"Complaints procedure"},{"href":"/government/organisations/homes-england/about/equality-and-diversity","title":"Equality and diversity"},{"href":"/government/organisations/homes-england/about/media-enquiries","title":"Media enquiries"},{"href":"/government/organisations/homes-england/about/modern-slavery-statement","title":"Modern slavery statement"},{"href":"/government/organisations/homes-england/about/access-and-opening","title":"Office access and opening times"},{"href":"/government/organisations/homes-england/about/our-governance","title":"Our governance"},{"href":"/government/organisations/homes-england/about/research","title":"Research at Homes England"},{"href":"/government/organisations/homes-england/about/statistics","title":"Statistics at Homes England"},{"href":"/government/organisations/homes-england/about/recruitment","title":"Working for Homes England"},{"href":"https://www.homesenglandcareers.co.uk","title":"Jobs"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/national-housing-bank-makes-significant-cornerstone-equity-investment-in-starlight-uks-build-to-rent-fund-ii","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a05ac1aee62840dba48a27c/s712_resized_960x640__1_.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a05ac1a22977ebc82cb3f69/s465_resized_960x640__1_.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6a05ac1a97000cb6073e4de4/resized_960x640__1_.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-05-12T15:54:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Starlight Investments and the National Housing Bank unite to accelerate rental housing: the bank’s phased investment of £100 million advances 6,000‑home pipeline through Starlight’s platform.</p>\n</div>","title":"National Housing Bank Makes Significant Cornerstone Equity Investment in Starlight UK’s Build-to-Rent Fund II"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/landmark-860m-joint-venture-between-homes-england-capitalcentric-and-swiss-life-asset-managers-makes-first-acquisition-in-manchester","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69d61c7ae99da92a6369df45/s712_11272_FERROUS_VIEW03_960x640.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69d61c7a62e15d2e4a46255a/s465_11272_FERROUS_VIEW03_960x640.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69d61c7a62e15d2e4a462559/11272_FERROUS_VIEW03_960x640.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-04-08T10:02:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Impact&amp;Places housing partnership is expected to deliver 2,250 homes across the UK.</p>\n</div>","title":"Landmark £860 million joint venture between Homes England, Capital&Centric and Swiss Life Asset Managers makes first acquisition in Manchester"},{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/national-housing-bank-and-aviva-to-invest-100-million-to-build-thousands-of-high-quality-family-homes-in-uk-towns-and-cities","image":{"alt_text":" Moston Lane, Manchester. Credit: MCAU.","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69cbbc142d120d9d5ec0f316/s712_moston_960_640.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69cbbc148017673ffec0f320/s465_moston_960_640.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69cbbc14b5ac47b0874f3f59/moston_960_640.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-03-31T13:00:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The first sites in Liverpool and Manchester will see 300 aspirational homes built on brownfield sites in well‑connected locations in boost to regional econo